data.description: Welcome home to 2447 River Rd, a Beautiful, Move-In Ready home with loads of updates!  The sunny, year round Florida room leads to the spacious living room/dining room combo and absolutely gorgeous kitchen with granite countertops, stainless steel appliances and great eat in area with sliding glass doors to deck and large, deep yard. Also, first floor laundry and updated half bath.  Three bedrooms and primary has walk-in closet.  Updated full bath with dual sink vanity. Central Air, Tankless Hot Water and two sheds.  (Very back 25 ft by width of property to be acquired by NYSDOT for multi-use trail summer of 2024. Privacy fence will be installed by NYSDOT.)  Square footage adjusted to reflect measurements of appraiser.
